Deg [[tusnakt]], '''Amaɣad''' yettwaglam d azlem aɣɣad ilan (yesɛan) [[teɣzi]] timifedt d [[tehri]] yettfakkan s 0, akken i yegber seg wuṭṭun ur n-ttfakka n [[agaz (tanzeggit)|wagazen]]. Ma deg [[tanzeggit taklidant|tenzeggit taklidant]], yella yiwen n umaɣad itekk-d seg sin n wagazen deg tallunt, akken i d-ittakk [[amaccaq|ameccaq]] wezzilen gar n yal n sin n wagazen. Dɣa amaɣud iteddu ɣer [[ifed|yifed]] seg snat n tamiwin.

Sin n imaɣaden deg [[agni (tanzeggit)|wegni]] zemren ad [[Amsideɣ (tusnak)|msidɣen]] neɣ ad mmidgen deg yiwen n wagaz, ma deg yilem zemren ad ilin d [[Izelman imezluga|imezluga]].

